# Built-in Result Filters

ASP.NET Core provides some built-in filter attributes.

## ResponseCache

```csharp
[ResponseCache(Duration = 60)]
public IActionResult Index()
{
    return View();
}
```

Caches the response for 60 seconds.

---

## AutoValidateAntiforgeryToken

```csharp
[AutoValidateAntiforgeryToken]
```

Validates anti-forgery tokens for unsafe HTTP methods.

