# Result Filters vs Action Filters

| Feature                     | Action Filter | Result Filter |
| --------------------------- | ------------- | ------------- |
| Executes Before Action      | Yes           | No            |
| Executes After Action       | Yes           | No            |
| Executes Before Result      | No            | Yes           |
| Executes After Result       | No            | Yes           |
| Can Access Action Arguments | Yes           | No            |
| Can Modify Response         | Limited       | Yes           |

---

# Result Filters vs Middleware

| Feature                    | Result Filter          | Middleware                       |
| -------------------------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| MVC Specific               | Yes                    | No                               |
| Access Controller/ViewData | Yes                    | No                               |
| Works Outside MVC          | No                     | Yes                              |
| Best For                   | Response customization | Global request/response handling |

